      <title>对冲基金在澳大利亚 2.6 万亿美元养老金池中失宠</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/hedge-funds-lose-favor-in-australia-s-2-6-trillion-pension-pot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着监管机构对澳大利亚养老基金的费用和业绩的审查日益严格，全球增长最快的退休资金池之一正在减少对对冲基金的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/hedge-funds-lose-favor-in-australia-s-2-6-trillion-pension-pot</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
